# Approach
We need to carry only 2 things:
1. What is current min
2. What numbers have been added

If queue is empty, then we just keep moving on straightly from 1 to inf increasing current value, otherwise we have added numbers, so we should pop them first of all form min to max, that is achieved by priority queue.

If it was helpfull, please like)

